        "action": "Bring back Sundays being a day of rest.",
        "additional_details": "This lockdown has reminded me of Sunday\u2019s when I was younger. No shops open except for essentials, less cars on the road, families out walking together. We all survived without Sunday trading and there seemed a lot less stress and mental illness back then.",
